    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Horses suitable for riding or light work, and of a size and build between a heavy horse and pony. Light horses are often classified according to their training, including riding horses, racers, trotters, and cow horses.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
